collections.name: The Missing CryptoQueen: The Truth They Tried to Bury
collections.description:
They called me the CryptoQueen. They said I built a $5 billion empire. Then they called me a fraud. A mastermind. A ghost.

For years, you’ve been told a story about OneCoin—one carefully crafted by those who needed a villain. They painted me as the face of the scam while the real masterminds walked free, hidden behind banks, governments, and secret deals.

But here’s what they never told you.

OneCoin wasn’t supposed to be a scam. I believed in it. And when I discovered the truth, I became a threat. That’s when they turned on me. That’s when I had to disappear.

For years, I’ve been silent. Watching. Gathering proof.

Now, it’s time to reveal what really happened—the secret deals, the betrayals, the people in power who never wanted this book to exist.

This is not just my story. This is the truth they tried to bury.

And once you know it, nothing will ever look the same again.

collections.name: World Coins
collections.description:
World Coins – The Future of Numismatics in Web3 🪙
Own a piece of history—both digital and real! This project brings historical coins into the blockchain, creating a unique bridge between numismatics and NFTs.
🔹 How It Works
Each NFT in this collection is tied to a real, historical coin that remains permanently within the project.
When you purchase an NFT, the physical coin is assigned to your wallet, but it is not physically transferred—instead, it stays as part of the World Coins collection, ensuring its preservation and future use.
As the NFT holder, you have decision-making power over the future virtual use, resale, integration, or development of your coin within the ecosystem.
🔹 Dynamic NFT Supply
If an identical coin (same year, mint, denomination) is added to the project, the NFT supply increases proportionally to the number of physical coins available.
Your NFT represents both digital ownership and a stake in the numismatic heritage secured within the project.

collections.name: Nullverse
collections.description:
NULLVERSE is a limited collection of only 50 unique glitch art NFTs. Initially, only 10 NFTs will be released. The remaining 40 NFTs will be created only if the first 10 are sold. With each sale, the artwork will degrade further, becoming more corrupted and enhancing the mystery of the collection.

This collection adds value not just to its owners but to each individual NFT they possess. Early buyers won’t just own a unique piece; they will contribute to the creation process of the remaining pieces. Every sale will increase the corruption, adding deeper layers of distortion, and continuously breaking the reality of the artwork.

NULLVERSE is an experience where reality is corrupted and digital art evolves. Owning an NFT in this collection is not just about having a digital asset; it’s about owning a key to the evolution of the entire collection.

Be a part of the journey – Buy the first 10 NFTs, and contribute to the creation of the remaining 40 pieces!
